xmpp_frontend Readme document
#############################

This is not an OTP release. It's just a "local" installation 
of ejabberd, with scripts to try and fix its hardcoded paths.

build (and make the releas)
###########################

    make release

This produces a distributable (to the same architecture as it 
was built on) directory containing ejabberd and our components
in >>> rel/xmpp_frontend <<<

install
#######

from the xmpp_frontend directory

    ./update-installation

Redo this step each time you move the location of xmpp_frontend
or erlang in your filesystem.

run
###

ejabberd-installation/sbin/ejabberdctl (start|stop)